00:09:13.006 --> 00:09:15.046 A:middle
that they're offering,
that spells it

00:09:15.046 --> 00:09:16.186 A:middle
out for you right away.

00:09:17.786 --> 00:09:19.296 A:middle
Now I don't know how
many of you notice

00:09:19.296 --> 00:09:21.336 A:middle
that there's also this
Get Premium button here

00:09:21.336 --> 00:09:22.126 A:middle
in the corner.

00:09:22.746 --> 00:09:26.626 A:middle
And if you did, would
