00:09:28.826 --> 00:09:31.866 A:middle
I mean, some of you might
have tapped on it to find out

00:09:31.866 --> 00:09:33.486 A:middle
and some of you may not have.

00:09:34.636 --> 00:09:36.696 A:middle
And they have the details
here about what you get.

00:09:37.646 --> 00:09:38.936 A:middle
But having this in addition

00:09:38.936 --> 00:09:42.936 A:middle
to that integrated message
is just much more effective

00:09:43.156 --> 00:09:46.816 A:middle
at explaining what the feature
does for you and offering it

00:09:46.886 --> 00:09:50.966 A:middle
to you at the time
that you can use it.

00:09:51.236 --> 00:09:54.016 A:middle
Just remember, don't
be this guy.

00:09:54.936 --> 00:09:58.636 A:middle
Nobody wants someone pushing
in your face pestering you.

00:09:59.756 --> 00:10:02.776 A:middle
Pestering people is not going to
get the results that you want.


WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:09:59.756 --> 00:10:02.776 A:middle
Pestering people is not going to
get the results that you want.

00:10:03.376 --> 00:10:05.746 A:middle
But thoughtful integration
of the merchandise will.

00:10:06.386 --> 00:10:11.916 A:middle
Now another challenge is to
help people understand the value

00:10:11.916 --> 00:10:13.026 A:middle
of what you're offering.

00:10:13.616 --> 00:10:16.076 A:middle
And if you walked
into a clothing store,

00:10:16.076 --> 00:10:17.596 A:middle
this is easy to figure out.

00:10:17.596 --> 00:10:21.256 A:middle
You can touch the merchandise,
feel what the fabric feels like.

00:10:21.926 --> 00:10:25.076 A:middle
Does it feel luxurious or
does it feel kind of cheap?

00:10:26.046 --> 00:10:26.846 A:middle
Is it well made?

00:10:27.026 --> 00:10:28.186 A:middle
Are the seams are falling apart?

00:10:29.156 --> 00:10:30.626 A:middle
Most importantly,
does it fit you?

00:10:30.956 --> 00:10:31.656 A:middle
Does it look good?

00:10:31.656 --> 00:10:33.026 A:middle
Is it going to suit
your purposes?

00:10:34.686 --> 00:10:36.166 A:middle
So letting people try

00:10:36.166 --> 00:10:39.656 A:middle
out merchandise before they buy
it is a really effective way

00:10:39.656 --> 00:10:42.636 A:middle
of helping them understand
the quality and the value

00:10:42.636 --> 00:10:45.256 A:middle
and the utility of
what you're offering.

00:10:46.176 --> 00:10:48.906 A:middle
I mean, you wouldn't buy
a car without taking it

00:10:48.906 --> 00:10:50.676 A:middle
for a test drive first, right?

