00:46:59.186 --> 00:47:02.046 A:middle
With all good design, it's
so important to iterate,

00:47:02.476 --> 00:47:05.056 A:middle
you want to measure the
success and quite frankly,

00:47:05.056 --> 00:47:07.126 A:middle
the failures of what you tried.

00:47:07.626 --> 00:47:09.676 A:middle
See how that has
an effect on things

00:47:10.056 --> 00:47:12.546 A:middle
and then make changes
based on those.

00:47:13.586 --> 00:47:16.276 A:middle
I mean, that all the things
that I mentioned today are going

00:47:16.276 --> 00:47:19.096 A:middle
to work for all product
types and all audiences.

00:47:19.816 --> 00:47:22.816 A:middle
So the more that you really fine
tune your approach, the better,

00:47:23.256 --> 00:47:26.036 A:middle
the more effective
it's going to be.

